EBRD Agrees on $40 Million Loan to Ukraine Gas Company Kubgas

-- B y   D a r y n a   K r a s n o l u t s k a
-- 
2011-05-20T10:16:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-20/ebrd-agrees-on-40-million-loan-to-ukraine-gas-company-kubgas.html
The European Bank for Reconstruction
and Development agreed on a $40 million loan to Kubgas, a
Ukrainian gas exploration and production company, to help
finance equipment purchases and improved energy saving.  The loan will be in two installments of $23 million and $17
million, the London-based bank said today in an e-mailed
statement.  Kubgas is majority owned by  Kulczyk Oil Ventures Inc. (KOV) , an
exploration company controlled by Polish billionaire Jan
Kulczyk.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Daryna Krasnolutska in Kiev at 
